    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "##  🔍Teacher Tip\r\nCheck out the **system prompt** for this chatbot.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Driving Chatbot\r\n\r\n### Do This\r\n\r\n1) **Predict:** What do you notice? What do you wonder? How do you expect the chatbot to respond?\r\n2) **Investigate:** Test the chatbot with at least 4 different messages\r\n3) **Reflect:** What worked like you expected? What surprised you?\r\n\r\nOnce you're finished, press the <code style=\"color:white; background-color:#7435b2\">Continue</code> button!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n::: details [**Click here to see example messages to try in this level**]\r\n* What are the requirements to get a driving permit?\r\n* What happens if you run a red light?\r\n:::\r\n\r\n&nbsp;",
